{
    "zh-CN": {
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_NAME": "纵火者",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "纵火者是一种短程坦克，使用火作为达到目的的手段。管理他的过热量表可以让他对成群的敌人造成大量伤害。平衡对于胜利至关重要。</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SUBTITLE": "疯狂纵火狂",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_NORMAL_GAUGE_NAME": "普通计量表",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_NORMAL_GAUGE_DESCRIPTION": "对白色部分造成 <style=cIsDamage>100%</style> 伤害。基础仪表具有抗过热能力。</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_GAUGE_NAME": "暴击计量表",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_BLUE_GAUGE_DESCRIPTION": "对白色部分造成 <style=cIsDamage>70%</style> 伤害，对蓝色部分造成 <style=cIsDamage>250%</style> 伤害。最大热量是固定的。</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_NAME": "龙息",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_DESCRIPTION": "发射一束火焰，造成 <style=cIsDamage>90% 伤害</style>。离目标越近，点火机会就越大。</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_NAME": "火球术",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>热度。 </style>发射火球，造成 <style=cIsDamage>225% 伤害并点燃 </style> 命中的敌人。</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ALT_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_NAME": "超速档",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ALT_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>热度。 </style><style=cIsUtility>Supercrit。 </style>发射火球，造成 <style=cIsDamage>160% 伤害并点燃 </style> 命中的敌人。</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_SCEPTER_NAME": "火风暴",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FIRESPRAY_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>热度。 </style>发射一束穿透性的强热光束，造成 <style=cIsDamage>300% 伤害并点燃 </style> 命中的敌人。如果持有时间较短，释放时会发射毁灭性光束，造成 <style=cIsDamage>450% 伤害</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_PUNCH_NAME": "零点爆炸",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_PUNCH_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热。 </style>推动自己前进，爆炸身后的敌人，造成 <style=cIsDamage>200% 伤害</style>。发射后立即与第一个敌人相撞，在周围爆炸中造成 <style=cIsDamage>200% 伤害</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_FLAREGUN_NAME": "信号枪",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SECONDARY_FLAREGUN_DESCRIPTION": "在 5 秒内发射一颗信号弹，造成 <style=cIsDamage>400% 伤害</style>，然后爆炸，造成 <style=cIsDamage>400% 伤害</style>，发射 5 颗信号弹，每颗造成 <style=cIsDamage>200% 伤害</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_UTILITY_CLEANSE_NAME": "净化",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_UTILITY_CLEANSE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热。 </style><style=cIsDamage>点燃</style>你周围的区域，对附近的敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>50%</style>伤害并消除其他状态效果。授予小幅速度提升.</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHIST_NAME": "受虐狂",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHIST_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>敏捷。热。 </style> 被 <style=cIsDamage>ignited</style> 造成的伤害转化为 <style=cIsHealing>healing</style> ，持续 6.5 秒。攻击速度提高 <style=cIsDamage>125%</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_NAME": "受虐狂",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_DESCRIPTION": "达到<style=cKeywordName>预期</style>限制后，定期对自己造成伤害以换取面积<style=cIsHealing>吸血</style>并燃烧。最多 10 秒后，<style=cIsDamage>Detonate</style>，然后 <style=cIsUtility>Overheat</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_SURGE_NAME": "怨恨",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_SPECIAL_MASOCHISM_SURGE_DESCRIPTION": "达到 <style=cKeywordName>Anticipation</style> 限制后，您移动速度更快并获得 <style=cKeywordName>Double Shot</style> 和 <style=cIsHealing>Lifesteal</style>。最多 10 秒后，<style=cIsDamage>Detonate</style>，然后 <style=cIsUtility>Overheat</style>.</style>0__",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_SCEPTER_NAME": "但丁的斥责",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PRIMARY_FLAMETHROWER_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION": "发射强烈光束，造成 <style=cIsDamage>140% 伤害</style>。离目标越近，点火机会就越大。如果按住 2 秒或更长时间，释放时发射最后一道光束，造成 <style=cIsDamage>150% 伤害</style>.</i>",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_ANTICIPATION": "<style=cKeywordName>预判</style>每失去和/或获得100热量,纵火者获得1层预判;获得5层后,他可激活受虐狂;额外层数增加伤害和持续时间;所有层数在结束时消耗。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_DETONATE": "<style=cKeywordName>引爆</style>纵火者爆炸,造成<style=cIsDamage>150%伤害</style>乘以累积的预判层数。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_LIFESTEAL": "<style=cKeywordName>生命偷取</style>纵火者在受虐狂激活时回复造成伤害的<style=cIsHealing>18%</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_MASO_SURGE_LIFESTEAL": "<style=cKeywordName>生命偷取</style>纵火者在怨恨激活时回复造成伤害的<style=cIsHealing>5%</style>。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_OVERHEAT_MASO": "<style=cKeywordName>过热:受虐狂</style>如果纵火者因热量积累过多而退出受虐狂,则应用EX过热,将其移动速度和伤害降低至70%。取消或让技能自然结束会应用过热,将其攻击速度降低至50%。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OVERHEAT_TEXT": "过热!",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_COOLING_TEXT": "冷却中...!",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_OVERHEAT_EX_TEXT": "过热:EX!",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME": "纵火狂热",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "抵抗所有来源的火焰伤害。将一次造成超过总生命值<style=cIsDamage>30%</style>的攻击转化为随时间造成的<style=cIsDamage>50%</style>火焰伤害。",
        "POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_KEYWORD_PYROMANIAPASSIVE": "除非虚弱已生效，否则纵火狂热不会影响坠落伤害。",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Arsonist: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Arsonist, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ECLIPSE5UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Arsonist: Grandmastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ECLIPSE5UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Arsonist, beat the game on Eclipse 5 or higher, OR beat the game on Typhoon (Starstorm 2 required).",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ECLIPSE8UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Arsonist: Survival",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ECLIPSE8UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Arsonist, beat the game on Eclipse 8, OR beat the game on Inferno (Inferno required).",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_FLAMETHROWERUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Arsonist: Pyromaniac",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_FLAMETHROWERUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Arsonist, beat a stage without overheating.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ARSONISTUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Embers",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_POPCORN_ARSONIST_BODY_ARSONISTUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "Kill a teleporter boss while it is ignited."
    }
